{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-all-timeline-js","path":"/2020/10/17/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"awesomeListRepo":"mourarthur/awesome-credit-modeling","categoryHTML":"<h2>Introduction</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.slideshare.net/YvanDeMunck/machine-learning-in-credit-risk-modeling-a-james-white-paper\">Machine Learning in Credit Risk Modeling</a> - James (formerly CrowdProcess) is a now-defunct online credit risk management startup that provided risk management tools to financial institutions. This whitepaper offers an overview of machine learning applications in the field of credit risk modeling.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-17T23:57:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"edm00se/awesome-board-games","categoryHTML":"<h2>Strategy</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/34635/stone-age\">Stone Age</a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>In Stone Age, players live in the early days of human history, competing for food and collecting resources to expand their tribe and achieve new levels of civilization. Take turns assigning your tribe members to limited areas on the board that benefit you in different ways, sequence your actions strategically and feed your people to avoid losing points or resources.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/itemrep/img/vApiI-gvXtwafEriPc4jDVJ1ajA=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic1632539.jpg\" alt=\"Stone Age\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">2 - 4</td>\n<td align=\"right\">10</td>\n<td align=\"right\">60-90m</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","updatedAt":"2020-10-17T23:49:08.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"rafaskb/awesome-libgdx","categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Visual Effects</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/crykn/libgdx-screen